  "title": "Sales Leader (Coaching Provided)",
  "description": "<p><strong><br>\n<br>\n🚀 Join Our High-Growth Team — Drive New Business and Build Lasting Relationships!</strong><br>\n<br>\n<br>\nWe’re on the lookout for driven, people-oriented individuals to support and introduce new customers to our clients.<br>\n<br>\nThis is an excellent opportunity if you’re ready to make a real impact in a fast-paced, high-growth environment. If you thrive on ownership, creativity, and collaboration, we want to hear from you!<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<strong><br>\n💡 What You’ll Bring</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Excellent communication skills.<br>\n</li>\n  <li>A genuine love for connecting with people.<br>\n</li>\n  <li>Self-motivation and a proactive attitude.<br>\n</li>\n  <li>The determination to turn a “no” into the next big “yes.”<br>\n<br>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>🌟 <strong>What We Offer</strong><br>\n</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>A supportive team that’s passionate about coaching and developing sales talent.<br>\n</li>\n  <li>Realistic goals, activity-based bonuses, and competitive commissions.<br>\n</li>\n  <li>Regular team and company social events — because we believe in celebrating wins together.<br>\n<br>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>If you’re ready to grow, learn, and make your mark — we’d love to speak with you!<br>\n<br>\n</strong></p>",
